    public class VectToGenPanel
extends UnitPanel
implements java.awt.event.ItemListener, java.awt.event.ActionListener, javax.swing.event.DocumentListener
    A RawToGenPanel UnitPanel to apply an interface for converting between the Raw data set and data analysis types within OCL, e.g. SampleSet, Sepctrum and their complex counterparts.
